<a href="/akira/dtd/3931-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3931">Mandatory Retirement Age for Government Employees&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8414-4049">eklahn</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">2 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Establish mandatory retirement age for civil servants, say 65.  Absolutely essential employees can be retained as contractors.</div>
